data.description: WELCOME HOME TO THIS VERY WELL MAINTAINED RAISED RANCH. THIS HOME HAS BEEN LOVED BY ONE FAMILY FOR ALMOST 30 YEARS! JUST WAITING FOR THE NEXT ONE TO CALL IT HOME. WALK INTO TO THE LARGE KITCHEN WITH STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES AND AN OPEN DINNING ROOM AND LIVING ROOM. FIRST FLOOR HAS TWO BEDROOMS AND A FULL BATH. BOTTOM LEVEL YOU WILL FIND ANOTHER BEDROOM WITH A SECOND LIVING ROOM OR FAMILY ROOM WITH A COZY FIREPLACE TO ENJOY IN THE COLDER MONTHS. COMPLETE WITH A LAUNDRY ROOM AND HALF BATH. WITH A SINGLE CAR ATTACHED GARGE YOU HAVE PLENTY OF SPACE FOR STORAGE OR TO STORE YOUR VEHICLE! WALK OUTSIDE TO YOUR VERY SPACIOUS BACKYARD WITH COMPLETE PRIVACY. LOCATION IS KEY WITH THIS HOME BEING CENTRALLY LOCATED JUST OFF OF 81 AND CLOSE TO ONEIDA RIVER! SCHEDULE YOUR PRIVATE VIEWING TODAY!
